{"tid":894680,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"前十字韌帶撕裂，點算好","createTime":"2018-11-08T14:34:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-14T09:37:51.000Z","uid":142964,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"53a7960979b42e9be85a04108098ab6d765c4fe2","tid":894680,"uid":142964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T14:34:59.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打試過前十字韌帶撕裂？<br />\n<br />\n腫就唔覺，但成兩星期都仲係酸軟有時驚冇力咁，行路正常慢跑ok，但感覺有d 唔穩。<br />\n<br />\n本身踢開波做開d 劇烈運動，請問係咪一定要做手術先掂？<br />\n<br />\n人生已完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f03d0d09821d2d8b5fadf2273d4702d25e03087","tid":894680,"uid":19186,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T14:48:56.000Z","msg":"照mri<br />\n做手術<br />\n做物理治療"},{"pid":"e1e44f92346771f4a7feaae551d1e66c53dfff99","tid":894680,"uid":206275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T14:49:33.000Z","msg":"康復中<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7088b38052a6759486d098013045e8b9b4be219","tid":894680,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T14:52:56.000Z","msg":"照咗MRI?"},{"pid":"8f28a511184aac3b408474bc4724d8db21a8a655","tid":894680,"uid":158472,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T14:59:57.000Z","msg":"我係斷裂+半月板撕裂<br />\n做咗手術7個月後踢番波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n三年後嘅今日依然踢緊波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e4166ab1e2d69d38552cc83b488028810d6360b","tid":894680,"uid":217852,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T15:12:23.000Z","msg":"岩岩做完10日...<br