pid":"8139ef16d45938828d330b151d92da2950e0805e","tid":894680,"uid":118881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f28a511184aac3b408474bc4724d8db21a8a655","tid":894680,"uid":158472,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T14:59:57.000Z","msg":"我係斷裂+半月板撕裂<br />\n做咗手術7個月後踢番波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n三年後嘅今日依然踢緊波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T08:40:35.000Z","msg":"做完手術7個月後踢返波咁快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n醫生同物理治療師都建議起碼一年先踢返<br />\n<br />\n不過想問問再做返劇烈運動個心理陰影大唔大？<br />\n好驚會再斷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T08:58:59.000Z","msg":"(消腫後)未做手術前我已經操緊四頭肌<br />\n做完後三個月開始隔日慢跑，六個月可以快跑<br />\n開頭實有陰影，但隨住操練同日子增多就知道咩動作係做到(即係有信心)。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca02fb47ab39a09fef3b79b3fbae8d58e817a34a","tid":894680,"uid":217852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8681eae40f5015b6a1ea728009d20824b89c9a9b","tid":894680,"uid":146581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1309b6a1b66d2e8affaf71e194dd03b1f92049d1","tid":894680,"uid":217852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a766067ffcbc95c3d82eb08fc2785f55c4038ed","tid":894680,"uid":146581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T09:09:21.000Z","msg":"斷左前十字 做完手術大約兩星期 仲未甩柺杖 進度係咪有d慢？ 想正常行翻路一般要幾耐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T17:31:12.000Z","msg":"應該正常，我之前兩次都係5-6星期甩拐杖。<br />\n人人情況唔同，最好問返物理治療師 / 醫生最準確<br />\n<br />\n加油！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T18:00:25.000Z","msg":"復健過程嘅心情好難過，多謝ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T16:36:32.000Z","msg":"I know that feel...<br />\n唯有就努力消腫先，消完腫再做下一步治療。<br />\n一步一步黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f62a46b507c03faff92c8c95568f47fce0d94577","tid":894680,"uid":217852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8139ef16d45938828d330b151d92da2950e0805e","tid":894680,"uid":118881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f28a511184aac3b408474bc4724d8db21a8a655","tid":894680,"uid":158472,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T14:59:57.000Z","msg":"我係斷裂+半月板撕裂<br />\n做咗手術7個月後踢番波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n三年後嘅今日依然踢緊波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T08:40:35.000Z","msg":"做完手術7個月後踢返波咁快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n醫生同物理治療師都建議起碼一年先踢返<br />\n<br />\n不過想問問再做返劇烈運動個心理陰影大唔大？<br />\n好驚會再斷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T16:46:54.000Z","msg":"會有心理陰影<br />\n第一次康復後(右腳)做返運動有d 動作會唔敢做，就住就住<br />\n不過一路操返，一路keep 住做運動就開始無諗咁多<br />\n到最後好似無傷過咁(心理上)<br />\n<br />\n不過第二次度復後(左腳)就完全唔敢跳盡，直到再整親<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae792e44c6262907b61a183600715098ac9d6602","tid":894680,"uid":196864,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T23:18:38.000Z","msg":"十字韌帶撕裂我都有 十幾年前<br />\n拆完石膏個陣隻腳伸唔返直 一想伸直痛到PK<br />\n要做半年物理治療 日日要壓腿<br />\n而家算係好返哂 腳可以伸直哂<br />\n但風濕一定有 企得耐菠蘿蓋亦會痛<br />\n個陣醫生話我知 十字韌帶撕裂算係永久傷殘<br />\n因為就算好返都返唔到100% 等如你個傷口好返有疤<br />\n條疤永遠係到會影響到韌帶<br />\n同埋以後做運動個陣都要帶腳套札住個菠蘿蓋"},{"pid":"bf82934ecc4019933a83b6f217cf41111cb58bd2","tid":894680,"uid":55458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae792e44c6262907b61a183600715098ac9d6602","tid":894680,"uid":196864,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T23:18:38.000Z","msg"